  "title": "Research & Advocacy Intern",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Duties and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>1.     Facilitation of research and content gathering on the following topics:</p><p>·      Violence against women</p><p>·      Women & ageing</p><p>·       Women in the workplace</p><p>·      Caregiving & Caregivers</p><p>·      Other gender-related topics and policies</p><p>2.  Support in preparation of presentations, speeches and talking points for interviews, events, and articles.</p><p>3.  Content and operational support for SCWO events, meetings, and international visits.<br /></p><p>*This is an internship</p>",
